1. Copy all the coupon codes from "Sample Coupons.txt"

2. Paste them in "Coupon PDF Format.docx"

3. Select the pasted coupons in the .docx file, make it bold and change the font to Calibri (Body), 15.

4. Select all the coupon codes in the .docx file again. Go to Layout Tab --> Columns --> Two Columns.

5. Select all the coupon codes in the .docx file again. Go to Insert Tab --> Table --> Convert Text to Table --> Columns = 2 --> Separate Text at Paragraph.

6. Select the table. Go to Table Layout, and set Height as 0.95cm and alignment as center.

7. Update the footer, with Generated Date, Validity Days and Expiry Date.